flowchart LR
    V[Video Windows] --> FB[FaceNet + Projection + BiLSTM + Attention]
    S[Signal Sequence] --> SB[Channel Attention + CNN + BiLSTM + Attention]
    FB --> CA[Cross-Modal Attention]
    SB --> CA
    CA --> FG[Soft Reliability Gating Fusion]
    FG --> CLF[Binary Valence Classifier]
    CLF --> OUT[Negative / Positive]
